platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Fast-paced, accessible, and utterly brilliant, Marvel Snaps quick, competitive matches are packed with seemingly infinite possibilities. Do you annoy opponents by dominating the first rounds playing field with Squirrel Girls rodent hordes? Or do you build your 12-card deck around the complementary card effects of the Guardians of the Galaxy? Theres no wrong answer. Fantastic animations, abilities, and art that perfectly channel the personality of the comics help make this one of the best card games on the App Store.
